---
title: Creamy Lemon Butter Bavette Steak with Parmesan Zucchini Rounds & Scallion Couscous
description: Lemon is our go-to ingredient for brightening up any meal, and this dish is positively bursting with citrusy goodness! Seared chicken is drizzled with a creamy, lemon-spiked pan sauce that would taste good on pretty much anything. On the side, there’s roasted zucchini topped with a crispy Parmesan topping—plus scallion-studded Israeli couscous tossed with both lemon juice and zest. When life gives you lemons, you know what to do.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6195595298529f7a49198e97-78a12483.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-lemon-butter-bavette-steak-6195595298529f7a49198e97-1475a62b.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/creamy-lemon-butter-bavette-steak-6195595298529f7a49198e97
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 970 kcal
